<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[سورة عبس <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> : الآيات ٢٥ الى ٣٤]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا الْماءَ صَبًّا <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا الْأَرْضَ شَقًّا <span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> فَأَنْبَتْنا فِيها حَبًّا <span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> وَعِنَباً وَقَضْباً <span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> وَزَيْتُوناً وَنَخْلاً <span class="c2">(٢٩)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَحَدائِقَ غُلْباً <span class="c2">(٣٠)</span> وَفاكِهَةً وَأَبًّا <span class="c2">(٣١)</span> مَتاعاً لَكُمْ وَلِأَنْعامِكُمْ <span class="c2">(٣٢)</span> فَإِذا جاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ <span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ الْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ <span class="c2">(٣٤)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٥-<span class="c5"> أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا الْماءَ صَبًّا:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا الْماءَ أنا أنزلنا الغيث من السماء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>صَبًّا إنزالا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢٦-<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا الْأَرْضَ شَقًّا:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا الْأَرْضَ بالنبات.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢٧-<span class="c5"> فَأَنْبَتْنا فِيها حَبًّا:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فِيها فى الأرض.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>حَبًّا يقتات به الناس.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢٨-<span class="c5"> وَعِنَباً وَقَضْباً:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَضْباً ونباتا يؤكل رطبا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٢٩-<span class="c5"> وَزَيْتُوناً وَنَخْلًا:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَزَيْتُوناً طيبا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَنَخْلًا مثمرا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٣٠-<span class="c5"> وَحَدائِقَ غُلْباً:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>غُلْباً ملتفة الأغصان.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٣١-<span class="c5"> وَفاكِهَةً وَأَبًّا:</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَفاكِهَةً وثمارا يتفكه بها.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَأَبًّا وعشبا تأكله البهائم.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٣٢-<span class="c5"> مَتاعاً لَكُمْ وَلِأَنْعامِكُمْ:</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>أي أنبتنا ذلك متاعا لكم ولأنعامكم.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٣٣-<span class="c5"> فَإِذا جاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ:</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>الصَّاخَّةُ صيحة القيامة التي تصم الآذان.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>٣٤-<span class="c5"> يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ الْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ:</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>